TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: --IIF ( --(Mtra_v = '2000' AND Stra_v = '0109') OR --(Mtra_v = '6000' AND Stra_v = '0117') OR --(Mtra_v = '0001' AND Stra_v = '0102') OR --(Mtra_v = '0001' AND Stra_v = '0106') --,1,0) --MTra (main) and STra (sub) are the following combinations: -- 0001/0102 -- 2000/0109 -- 6000/0117 -- 0001/0106 --Mtra_v, Stra_v
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Ind_MtraStra_v

, 0))
